PrecisReappointment of KAREN SUE BRENNAN of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a full-time member of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year; and order that KAREN SUE BRENNAN be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective February 15, 2004.
